7. Deployment creation?

USERS > DEPLOYMENT > Replica Set > POD

Auto healing & Auto scaling cannot be achieved through pod creation.
Deployment will create replica set and replica set will take care on auto healing process using kubernetes. 
Controller will moinitor the pod status and ensure the desired state with actual state.

# kubectl apply -f deployment.yml
